@MyProject_HostAddress = http://localhost:5294

### Dev login stub — exchange an email for a JWT. Seeded users below.
### alice=initiator, bob=Engineering manager (stage 1), carol=Dept Head (stage 2),
### dan=HR (stage 3), admin=WorkflowAdmin.

# @name loginAlice
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "alice@example.com" }

###
@alice = {{loginAlice.response.body.token}}

# @name loginBob
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "bob@example.com" }

###
@bob = {{loginBob.response.body.token}}

# @name loginCarol
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "carol@example.com" }

###
@carol = {{loginCarol.response.body.token}}

# @name loginDan
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "dan@example.com" }

###
@dan = {{loginDan.response.body.token}}

# @name loginAdmin
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@example.com" }

###
@admin = {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

### Who am I (diagnostic — shows claims + role mapping)
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/auth/whoami
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

### ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
### HAPPY PATH: create -> submit -> approve x3 -> Approved
### ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# @name createLeave
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/leave-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "fromDate": "2026-08-01", "toDate": "2026-08-05", "reason": "Summer vacation" }

###
@leaveId = {{createLeave.response.body.id}}

# @name submitLeave
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/leave-requests/{{leaveId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}

###
@instanceId = {{submitLeave.response.body.id}}

### Document is now locked (isLocked=true) once the outbox dispatcher runs
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/leave-requests/{{leaveId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}

### Alice is NOT the stage-1 approver -> 403
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/approvals/{{instanceId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ }

### Stage 1 (Manager = Engineering dept manager Bob) approves -> advances to Department Head
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/approvals/{{instanceId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{bob}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "comment": "Approved by manager" }

### Stage 2 (Department Head role = Carol) approves -> advances to HR Approval
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/approvals/{{instanceId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{carol}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ }

### Stage 3 (HR user = Dan) approves -> Approved (terminal)
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/approvals/{{instanceId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{dan}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ }

### Full immutable audit trail
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/approvals/{{instanceId}}/history
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}

### ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
### REJECT -> EDIT -> RESUBMIT (new cycle, history preserved)
### ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# @name createLeave2
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/leave-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "fromDate": "2026-09-01", "toDate": "2026-09-03", "reason": "Conference" }

###
@leaveId2 = {{createLeave2.response.body.id}}

# @name submitLeave2
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/leave-requests/{{leaveId2}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}

###
@instanceId2 = {{submitLeave2.response.body.id}}

### Reject at stage 1 (comment required)
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/approvals/{{instanceId2}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{bob}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "comment": "Dates clash with the release; please reschedule." }

### Owner edits the rejected document (allowed while Rejected)
PUT {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/leave-requests/{{leaveId2}}
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "fromDate": "2026-09-15", "toDate": "2026-09-17", "reason": "Conference (rescheduled)" }

### Resubmit -> new cycle 2, back to stage 1, prior history preserved
POST {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/approvals/{{instanceId2}}/resubmit
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}

### History now shows cycle 1 (submit/reject) AND cycle 2 (resubmit)
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/approvals/{{instanceId2}}/history
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}

### ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
### DASHBOARDS
### ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Bob's approval queue ("waiting on me")
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/my-pending
Authorization: Bearer {{bob}}

### Alice's documents
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/my-documents
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}

### SLA breaches (current pending stages past their SLA)
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/sla-breaches
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

### Per-workflow metrics
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/workflows/1/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

### ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
### ADMIN: workflow configuration (WorkflowAdmin role required)
### ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### List document types
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/document-types
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

### List workflows (with stages)
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/workflows
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

### Reorder stages of workflow 1 (example: reverse to 3,2,1)
PUT {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/workflows/1/stages/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "orderedStageIds": [3, 2, 1] }

### Non-admin hitting an admin endpoint -> 403
GET {{MyProject_HostAddress}}/api/workflows
Authorization: Bearer {{alice}}
